/*******************************************************************************
* File Name: cy_srff_v1_0.v
* Version `$CY_MAJOR_VERSION`.`$CY_MINOR_VERSION`
*
* Description:
* The SR Flip Flop component stores a digital value that can be set and reset.
* The verilog is generated by the CustomizeVerilog method in the CyCustomizer
* class in custom.cs.
*
********************************************************************************
* I*O Signals:
********************************************************************************
*   Name        Direction       Description
*   q           output          Stored value.
*   clk         input           When output may change.
*   s           input           Set value to '1'.
*   r           input           Reset value to '0'.
